      <title>[알립니다] 우리 아이 출생 소식 액자에 담아 간직하세요</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/special/announcement/2025/07/18/F4RPMD26N5HORGCTR6OYZKLT5Y/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/special/announcement/2025/07/18/F4RPMD26N5HORGCTR6OYZKLT5Y/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
      <description/>
